::Reptilica/Bloodystrike::

The two males' eyes slide down to Desmonus' hips as she swings them, 
both of them jerking their eyes back to her face as they hear her 
words.

"Its this way," Reptilica says, pointing down a hallway, turning 
around to leave in that direction when Bloodystrike speaks up.

"Idiot, its down this way."

Reptilica turns around, feeling extremely stupid when he realizes that 
Bloodystrike was right.

"Yes, er, well, shall we go to it then?" he asks, walking up to 
Desmonus and attempting to slide an arm around her, Bloodystrike doing 
the same from the other side.
